--></style><span style="font-size: 18px"><b>The Pontian Greek Society of Chicago Hosts Conference on the Asia Minor Catastrophe </b></span></p>
<div style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 1in 0pt 0in">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: center; line-height: normal; margin: 0in 1in 0pt 0in"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt"><img alt="" style="width: 416px; height: 272px" src="/images/media_files/media/lectures/academic%20conference%200631_opt.jpg" />&nbsp;</span></b></div>
<div style="line-height: normal; margin: 0in 1in 0pt 0in">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: center; line-height: normal; margin: 0in 1in 0pt 0in">From Left to Right:<br />
Dr. Van Coufoudakis, Dr. Taner Akcam, Historian&nbsp;Matthias Bjornlund, Judge James Booras, President George Mavropoulos, Dr. Constantine Hatzidimitriou, Dr. Alexander Kitroeff, Mr George Shirinian</div>
<div style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal; margin: 0in 1in 0pt 0in"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt"><br />
</span></b>&nbsp;F<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0)">or more information please contact the Society by email at 
 <script language='JavaScript' type='text/javascript'>
 <!--
